high_descs: Head towards the cabinet turn right to reach the cabinet on the right side.
Pick the ladle from the table.
Turn around and take right the sink.
Put the ladle on the sink and pour the water and clean it.
Pick the cleaned spoon from the cabinet and Turn around and take turn right.
Put the clean ladle on the top cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ladle on the wooden cabinet.

high_descs: Head rotate and walk near the cabinet.
Pick the spoon from the sink.
Head rotate and turn left to the ladle.
Rinse it well and pick it back from the cabinet.
Place the ladle inside the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: To place the ladle inside the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and enter into the cabinet.
Pick up the ladle off of the counter
Walk toward your right to the sink area.
Turn on the water and rinse off the ladle.
Take the spoon out of the sink and open the cabinet above you.
Put the ladle in the cabinet and close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: The robot should get the ladle off of the counter, wash it, and put it in the cabinet above.
